      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把PENDING到ARCHIVED的自动归档加上去了。现在APPROVED内部需要展开详细流程吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APPROVED",
        "ARCHIVED"
